snippet.title: Obsidian Legion - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The first official trailer for Obsidian Legion!

Embark on a dark journey in Obsidian Legion. 
Rise to the challenge as you fight your way in a land of perils and wonders. 
Explore the world and collect the tools necessary to overcome the many obstacles set before you.

Wishlist it now on Steam ▶ https://bit.ly/3HvOSHi

Twitter ▶ https://twitter.com/MantisFRK
Instagram ▶ https://www.instagram.com/obsidian_legion_game/
